title: "CodeFactor/Complexity: decompose runCreate (CC 172) and the audit-scope update guard (CC 38)"
description: "Eliminate the largest CodeFactor 'Complex Method' finding in the repo — runCreate (CC 172, src/cli/commands/create.ts) — plus the audit-scope guard enforceAllowAuditUpdateScope (CC 38, src/cli/commands/update.ts), behavior-preservingly. Decompose into pure, well-named, fully-docstringed helpers; prune eslint-suppressions.json for both functions; keep 100% coverage and contracts/full.json byte-identical. runUpdate (77), the update mutate apply-callback (148), and the register-mutation MCP arrows (18-28) are tracked as the follow-up stage."
